---
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
  <div class="md:col-span-1 space-y-2">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter mb-6">Operations</h2>
    <div class="data-border bg-[var(--neon-cyan)]/10 p-4 border-l-4 border-l-[var(--neon-cyan)]">
      <span class="text-[var(--neon-cyan)] font-bold block mb-1">01. MODELS</span>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Filter by capability, price, context. 85+ providers. RTFO indicators.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="data-border bg-slate-900/30 p-4 border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-slate-400 transition-all">
      <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold block mb-1 uppercase text-sm">02. Benchmarks</span>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">H2H tables, scatter plots, radar charts. ~400 entries.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="data-border bg-slate-900/30 p-4 border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-slate-400 transition-all">
      <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold block mb-1 uppercase text-sm">03. Agents</span>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Version detection, GitHub releases, changelogs, service health.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="data-border bg-slate-900/30 p-4 border-l-4 border-l-transparent hover:border-l-slate-400 transition-all">
      <span class="text-slate-400 font-bold block mb-1 uppercase text-sm">04. STATUS</span>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-mono">Live health for 22 providers. Incidents, maintenance, gauges.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="md:col-span-3 data-border bg-slate-900/50 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8 items-center">
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 aspect-square data-border bg-black p-2">
      <img alt="models TUI interface" class="w-full h-full object-cover" src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}models-screenshot.png`} />
    </div>
    <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
      <p class="text-2xl font-light text-white leading-tight mb-6">Real-time ingestion of 4,000+ model definitions across 85+ providers from models.dev.</p>
      <ul class="font-mono text-xs text-[var(--neon-cyan)] space-y-2 uppercase">
        <li>+ Filter by capability and price</li>
        <li>+ Sort by date, cost, context</li>
        <li>+ Cross-provider search</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
